{"tid":925650,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打試過自己換偈油","createTime":"2018-12-03T01:44:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T10:31:01.000Z","uid":6532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"965b3ff8177842b6d503f2f045d4b2cc88312a9b","tid":925650,"uid":6532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T01:44:14.000Z","msg":"澳洲換一次油要百幾澳紙, 準備自己買油同吸油器換, 有咩要注意? 已經搵到地方收集廢油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67b6cf970131d8603db6601f76cd0ea8310996e2","tid":925650,"uid":149908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"965b3ff8177842b6d503f2f045d4b2cc88312a9b","tid":925650,"uid":6532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T01:44:14.000Z","msg":"澳洲換一次油要百幾澳紙, 準備自己買油同吸油器換, 有咩要注意? 已經搵到地方收集廢油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T01:46:46.000Z","msg":"係個式到放晒D油, 再倒新油同換油隔 ( youtube好多教學, 跟返車款去SEARCH)"},{"pid":"e98bbf245112af89b3347f1299b571a1d89af065","tid":925650,"uid":152141,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"965b3ff8177842b6d503f2f045d4b2cc88312a9b","tid":925650,"uid":6532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T01:44:14.000Z","msg":"澳洲換一次油要百幾澳紙, 準備自己買油同吸油器換, 有咩要注意? 已經搵到地方收集廢油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T02:03:55.000Z","msg":"我都係睇youtube學試過一次<br />\n唔太難"},{"pid":"3dd166a604db9c504b0e03dde76ca2458c4d6fc1","tid":925650,"uid":6532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T02:49:08.000Z","msg":"好, 準備試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bf147fa93f8cd15feed0db1350ead8cf222cb2b","tid":925650,"uid":13878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T02:53:04.000Z","msg":"1) 首先了解下你架車有無油底螺絲<br />\n如果有, 即係可以放, 係車底放, 咁就唔洗吸油器"},{"pid":"6aa6e6883abc60731e55d80eea0c1bbd0bf4d717","tid":925650,"uid":13878,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T02:54:54.000Z","msg":"2) 買定你所需既材料先<br />\n<br />\n- 機油 (度數跟番原裝啦) (預多少少, 睇下你架車用幾多L)<br />\n- 機油格<br />\n- 漏斗<br />\n- 一個大而扁既盆 (如果有油底螺絲可以放的話) / 相反無就要買吸油器"},{"pid":"576185217016bd35e52055a3d50bf871bed40dba","tid":925650,"uid":158832,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:37:44.000Z","msg":"油底縲絲小心扭撻角同滑牙<br />\n盡量水平咁扭佢，食住d角，唔好斜<br />\n<br />\n鬆螺絲一般都要用力d, 唔夠力就搵野駁長架撐，用d水喉通都得<br />\n上螺絲就細力d，用一般架撐扭到頂盡就得，太大力會滑牙<br />\n<br />\n油同偈油格通常都一齊換<br />\n油格小心瀉到周圍係<br />\n<br />\n放完油，換完油格，再入偈油<br />\n私家車一般都4升偈油咁上下，隻隻車有d出入<br />\n未入油千祈唔好著車，唔係就成副車頭報銷<br />\n<br />\n入完之後，著左車，偈油流埋落油格先可以用油尺度得準<br />\n<br />\n著緊車係度唔準，車會震，d偈油會彈上油尺<br />\n一般都係熄車後5分鍾先度得準<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好貪多偈油，起油尺兩個圈or mark位之間就ok，一般係入到近頂果個圈<br />\n<br />\n利申：汽車機修學徒"},{"pid":"5b9cc679e7cd806b64b4ab664b825ba574e2db38","tid":925650,"uid":6532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:42:36.000Z","msg":"唔該咁多巴打解答, 都係準備買吸油器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 車尾箱個jack應該升唔到咁高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋個filter係上面, 所以都係嚮上面搞算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff5f823de1b0aafad8be2a0130b0532c906f6a62","tid":925650,"uid":158832,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5b9cc679e7cd806b64b4ab664b825ba574e2db38","tid":925650,"uid":6532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:42:36.000Z","msg":"唔該咁多巴打解答, 都係準備買吸油器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 車尾箱個jack應該升唔到咁高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋個filter係上面, 所以都係嚮上面搞算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:50:27.000Z","msg":"有條片，希望幫倒你<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Ebu2LVj1gEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEbu2LVj1gEA&d=j2VufJ7sHyWA%2BEuaD8bPOW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=17bd78e0\" data