%2Fimg%2Ffumoto-f106sx-m14-15-sx-series-drain-valve_1159255_500.jpg&h=1866a1c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁你以後換油就快好多同用少左工具。"},{"pid":"90cdd0f97a5171cb0a8571a2d6970acb3b0dc1ed","tid":925650,"uid":105366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T21:13:57.000Z","msg":"如果懶手動jack車既話可以考慮買呢舊野(我用緊)<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/61LIDtqiNhL._SX425_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F61LIDtqiNhL._SX425_.jpg&h=51e6d7fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但記住jack起左之後一定要落jack stand<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/81y9P8S7IVL._SL1500_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F81y9P8S7IVL._SL1500_.jpg&h=9c32e813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n性命猶關，咪慳。"},{"pid":"dad1a328bf24745503d84617bc34c4509298f0ca","tid":925650,"uid":141551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T06:13:23.000Z","msg":"記得check齊唔齊架生先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 試過奶野"},{"pid":"8be6ba9d9cf9265fe726e67af50b29cae014517a","tid":925650,"uid":40874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T07:46:08.000Z","msg":"另外如果油底鏍絲係膠既話記住換個新既上去，仲要跟鎊"},{"pid":"02b3d9e0439d47ae93033e565f50b09837d80520","tid":925650,"uid":158920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T10:31:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}